}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Tries to lock <code>rec_mutex</code>. If <code>rec_mutex</code> is already locked
by another thread, it immediately returns <code>false</code>. Otherwise
it locks <code>rec_mutex</code> and returns <code>true</code>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.32</p>
